{"tid":840555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中醫或能躋身主流療法 首次被世衞納入全球醫學綱要","createTime":"2018-09-29T01:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T01:54:36.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2328426eebaf2ddc736bbcb5938908ba4813bbba","tid":840555,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"中醫或能躋身主流療法 首次被世衞納入全球醫學綱要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據英國《自然》期刊日前報道，世衞組織世界衞生大會將於2019年推出第11版醫學綱要，首次納入中醫傳統醫學，意味中醫或在全球躋身主流療法，再非是僅為手術、放射治療等以外的補充替代療法。<br />\n<br />\n全球醫學綱要亦被稱為「國際疾病與相關健康問題統計分類」（ICD），在全球範圍擁有極大的影響力。ICD會對數千種疾病和診斷進行分類，決定100多個國家的診療過程，不但影響醫生診斷、保險公司的保險覆蓋範圍，亦影響流行病學家的相關研究。據了解，新納入的中醫傳統醫學相關資訊，將在第11版ICD第26章內，該章節主要闡釋傳統醫學的分類體系，會於2022年在世衞組織成員國間實施。<br />\n<br />\n據指，中醫傳統醫學將被納入ICD的工作，始於十多年前。2004年開始，時任世衞馬尼拉西太平洋辦事處傳統醫學顧問Choi Seung-hoon帶領亞洲國家數十名代表，將數千年來的中醫知識整理成一個清晰完整的構架體系。雖然接下來的數年時間，中國、日本、韓國等國家代表都曾在會議中針鋒相對，都認為本國版本才是正統中醫，應寫入目錄。最終這些代表都能逐步達成共識，提出包括3,106個術語的清單，然後對清單進行英文繙譯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180928/58733488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58733488&d=HfsGu98mWmxfAKfnpc4x7eI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5b14dfdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58733488&h=314d0f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180928/58733488</a>"},{"pid":"500e800158c81a464b9d45889aaba41034cf2233","tid":840555,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"世衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知比中國滲透啦"},{"pid":"43322ce64523f0ddc5f6b82e1ca72a217dd90709","tid":840555,"uid":5715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"500e800158c81a464b9d45889aaba41034cf2233","tid":840555,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"世衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知比中國滲透啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"上次仲讚中國疫苗把關好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7c2c67545fbacb6e3b6ff70f3e1b206efef5e1","tid":840555,"uid":105995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac93b7bdd6371013d207edfa0340312b3837833","tid":840555,"uid":39381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:37:46.000Z","msg":"自己批比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ba6f668bb6c4341924743a15d16c378192b8d6","tid":840555,"uid":120852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43322ce64523f0ddc5f6b82e1ca72a217dd90709","tid":840555,"uid":5715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"500e800158c81a464b9d45889aaba41034cf2233","tid":840555,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"世衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知比中國滲透啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"上次仲讚中國疫苗把關好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:39:08.000Z","msg":"結果就爆單假疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f669bce81b00df63ead156bfd9f9dadbd88502","tid":840555,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"巫醫都可以入主流療法，依個世界真係反智"},{"pid":"aee19ecaf3126b2a68671cddabb7de465b0b7ead","tid":840555,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4b4c9d025e6e78bf214220fb1c3cb91dc8be9d7","tid":840555,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}